underlying_goal: Initialize a read-only exploration agent and confirm its understanding of project state and constraints.
primary_success: The agent gave a comprehensive summary of the project, its personal constraints (read-only, zero-tolerance rules), and a clear menu of how it could help.
brief_summary: A thorough warmup session where the agent demonstrated a deep understanding of the project. It summarized the paper's topic, the core C3 method, its read-only constraints, and research methodology principles it would follow.
